text.tspan: My husband and I absolutely enjoyed our stay at Crown Plaza Hotel in Times Square Manhattan. Although I have visited other
Crown Plaza’s locations, this particular location has confirmed that all of their chain of locations are all phenomenal.
cleanliness, exclusive lobby area, awesome location, and outstanding customer service (Freddy was the best!); I will definitely
make this my number one pick when choosing a hotel in New York. I can return again and again. Therefore, I highly recommend
